{"tid":1831770,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[溫故知新]衛生部部長張文康表示，疫情已經得到有效控制，在中國、北京工作、旅遊是安全的，戴不戴口罩都安全","createTime":"2020-01-20T15:45:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-21T03:20:59.000Z","uid":239696,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4590fcec3d82e9ce442fe46f063491f1ba2114c5","tid":1831770,"uid":239696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T15:45:26.000Z","msg":"他說北京當時SARS病例只有12例，死亡3例，還笑著說，<span style=\"color: red;\">戴不戴口罩都是安全的</span>。張文康還指出SARS是指在中國大陸得到有效控制，沒有說有效消滅徹底消滅，也沒有說在世界各地有效控制和完全消滅。在解釋衛生部為什麼不通報疫情時說，非典型肺炎並不是法定傳染病原不屬於必須報告範圍；疫情只發生在局部地區，《傳染病防治法》規定由發生疫情的地方政府公佈也就是廣東省政府。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最後北京有2434人感染，147人死 (靠著中國既強大醫療技術，死亡百分比遠低於其他先進國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)</span>"},{"pid":"5cb12d2e9abfa9cea41ef7be159ba2cccc960ba3","tid":1831770,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T03:18:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aad43ab81bc48014945ca9a81723ac63b7dd8880","tid":1831770,"uid":90328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T03:20:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 沒事兒"},{"pid":"8a8f5e30af843022c2fa207077fc19b4c9339174","tid":1831770,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T03:20:59.000Z","msg":"推 中國人絕不戴口罩！<br />\n戴口罩是反中共,支持武漢獨立<br />\n認同請分享<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nPUdy8k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnPUdy8k.jpg&h=4d93e1d3&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}